            <thetext>When a TabView has overflow scrolling of its tabs, the scroll effect is 
minuscle, e.g. one click only scrolls a few pixels to either side. It is 
tedious to make sufficient progress. Also, this way tabs are displayed halfway 
visible which is usually not really helpful. A better way would be scrolling 
tab-wise, with each click stepping the full tab width which comes into view so 
it is completely visible.</thetext>
